ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with Global Child Care Services ** NCC **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant one option of five years, commencing on February 1, 2015, to extend an existing lease with GLOBAL CHILD CARE SERVICES to occupy a property located at 1425 and 1431 ST. JOSEPH BOULEVARD in Ottawa.
